{
  "document_background": {
    "page_sections": [
      {
        "source_section": "集團首席執行官兼總裁報告",
        "target_section": "Group Chief Executive and President's Report",
        "content_type": "ceo_report",
        "page_range": [
          12,
          16
        ]
      }
    ],
    "roles": [
      {
        "source": "李源祥",
        "target": "Lee Yuen Cheung",
        "role": "Group Chief Executive and President"
      }
    ],
    "terms": [],
    "style_rules": [
      "Use US$ for U.S. dollar amounts.",
      "Keep listed-company annual report disclosure tone formal and publishable.",
      "Do not change numbers, percentages, years, named entities or financial metric values.",
      "Use established financial abbreviations for table labels when provided.",
      "Keep row and column semantics unchanged.",
      "Use n/m for 無意義."
    ]
  },
  "current_unit": {
    "page_no": 16,
    "unit_id": "p16_g02",
    "unit_mode": "semantic_group",
    "slot_count": 4,
    "source_text": "在2020年，2019冠狀病毒病大流行無疑是我們生活記憶中最大規模的公共衞生緊急狀態。受影響的企業和家庭\n獲得前所未見的公共財政和金融支援，有助緩解由疫情大流行造成的部分極端金融衝擊，並加快復甦步伐，這在\n具備完善衞生政策及基建的國家尤其可見。然而，各國之間存在顯著差異，在這困境下，亞洲（日本除外）地區\n錄得全球相對最強勁的國內生產總值表現。現時，環球經濟正剛剛開始擺脫一場深度衰退，並步入好轉的初步階",
    "current_translation": "In 2020, the COVID-19 pandemic was undoubtedly the largest-scale public health emergency in our living memory. Affected businesses and households received unprecedented public financial and financial support, which helped mitigate some of the extreme financial impacts caused by the pandemic and accelerated the pace of recovery, which was particularly evident in countries with well-established health policies and infrastructure. However, there were significant differences between countries, and under these challenging circumstances, Asia (excluding Japan) recorded the relatively strongest gross domestic product performance globally. Currently, the global economy is just beginning to emerge from a deep recession and entering the initial stages of improvement."
  },
  "output_format": {
    "translations": [
      {
        "unit_id": "p16_g02",
        "translation": "<更紧凑译文>"
      }
    ]
  }
}

